column5: Beautiful cul-de-sec home surrounded by golf course. Our lovely & private 1 BD, 1 BA, & throughout our home is decorated with antiques and home decor from all over the world. Come stay with us and experience the entire world in comfort. Huge patio to hang out . Close by to lake park and down town McKinney. Convenient access to Hwy 75 and 121- within 1 mile from HWY,
